summary: Adds a mansion near the south of the Nightgate Inn. First mod for Skyrim.
descriptionHtml:
[center][font=Lucida Sans Unicode][b][color=#ff0000][size=4]Mod officially no longer supported as of 7/14/2014[/size][/color][/b][/font][/center][center][font=Lucida Sans Unicode]-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------[/font][/center][font=Lucida Sans Unicode]My first house mod for Skyrim, it definitely isn't my best work so please feel free to check my other work :)

I can't remember anything about this mod, sorry, but I do know it's a house somewhere near Nightgate Inn (or whatever it's called.) The reason I keep this up because I noticed I've been getting more endorsements and downloads on it lately, which is odd, so it will stay up.

[b][size=3].: Change Log:.[/size][/b]
4/26/2015 - Is now a modder's resource.

[b][size=3].: Credits :.[/size][/b]
'Modders Resource Pack' by Oaristys and Tony67
'PotionShelf, BookSets, OpenBooks, and FoodContainer Resources' by Blary
'Paintings and Frames' by Artisanix
- Bethesda
- Creation Kit

[b][size=3].: License :.[/size]
[/b]You are not allowed to use any of my assets or the assets within for your own commercial use (which means you're making profit off mine and others work.)
You can however modify this mod to how you see fit as long as it remains free and on the Nexus. Essentially this can be considered a modder's resource because I have no intent on continuing this particular mod. Remember to credit myself and the work of those within.
[/font]
author: LethalThreat
